In this repo we will learn how to automate your browser with selenium?

#First of all we will import the modules that are needed to automation,
#We will start from basic level
 ---------------------------------------
 First of all you have to install browser driver to autmate it.
 Here are the links of drivers:-
 ---> see your browser version then install it.
        -->https://chromedriver.chromium.org/downloads
        -->https://github.com/mozilla/geckodriver/releases
        -->https://developer.microsoft.com/en-us/microsoft-edge/tools/webdriver/
        
  ############# Chrome Browser ###########################
  
  from selenium import webdriver
  driver=webdriver.Chrome()
  # write the path of python file
  path=r"C:\Users\Muhammad\PycharmProjects\pythonProject\file.py"
  driver.get("https://www.saucedemo.com/")
 
  ############# Firefox Browser ############################
  
  from selenium import webdriver
  driver=webdriver.Firefox()
  # write the path of python file
  path=r"C:\Users\Muhammad\PycharmProjects\pythonProject\file.py"
  driver.get("https://www.saucedemo.com/")
  ############# Microsoftedge Browser ########################
  
  from selenium import webdriver
